9","tid":1418012,"uid":261435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">微訊群<br />\n<br />\n福建呀叔落到街俾黑衣人用福建話屌返轉頭<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FaTvrfUcjZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFaTvrfUcjZM&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=308b8bb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FaTvrfUcjZM</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"哇屌竟然係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開頭講野個阿叔應該識打人個幾個福建幫，佢話：&rdquo;打輸左喇 打輸左喇！屌佢老味⋯遊行入面混左個班係自己福建人嚟嘅⋯⋯班仆街混左入遊行人士度帶人返自己北角搞搞陣，捉到一個喺度打先講福建話話係自己人&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n佢意思係想話放風叫佢去等黑衫打黑衫係比人跌9左，原來係有幾個福建鬼混左入遊行人士入面引其他黑衫人去北角同佢哋打！<br />\n<br />\n好撚鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14058229ba0277f96628b14ee9538e6145a48eaf","tid":1418012,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:34:30.000Z","msg":"屌 呢個要廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80929a6071389a1a9599f3fe56492c7966b3c253","tid":1418012,"uid":280311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:37:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}